{"tid":521582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"MH370客機　馬來西亞重啟搜索","createTime":"2018-01-06T16:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T01:47:03.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b4cfba655f511f443b104842e0adee0614e36836","tid":521582,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/003537_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F003537_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e781c743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬航 MH 370 客機失蹤至今接近 4 年，馬來西亞政府宣佈，重啟搜索工作。<br />\n<br />\n大馬交通部部長廖中萊周六宣佈，批准總部位於美國的海底勘探公司「無限海洋」Ocean Infinity，派出一艘研究船搜索客機。<br />\n<br />\n研究船正由南非前往南印度洋，預料二月初抵達，會搜索二萬五千平方公里範圍。<br />\n<br />\n勘探公司承諾，只會在發現客機殘骸後，才收取費用。<br />\n<br />\nMH 370 客機於 2014 年 3 月，接載 239 名乘客及機組人員，由吉隆坡起飛前往北京，但起飛後沒多久，便與控制塔失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n中國、澳洲及馬來西亞去年一月結束有關搜索行動。"},{"pid":"5da0974d2d43d625ab7af08cc97d075c5fed900d","tid":521582,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d54b460b3fa7155fcde6560ca743fbccaa4df51","tid":521582,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T00:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08030ea97db9f89aeb3826190eee1cb6eb005f5f","tid":521582,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"沉左落海底點揾得番Y，吊架機上水面都無可能做到，諗起班乘客係水底浸左四年，變哂巨人觀，好恐怖"},{"pid":"30d9f5413e36da93c214a289ae6157fbc6d99ac9","tid":521582,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"呢架機係一個人類無法探索既地方 rip"},{"pid":"357c7f18cf7357b5e37ddef42143a5f4085f2971","tid":521582,"uid":32810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08030ea97db9f89aeb382619